title: Santa Catalina Omnium and Oracle Road Race
IC3 Tucson Crit Training Series #1
description: Series of 5 days of crit training rides. Each day will have 3 training rides meant for beginner, intermediate, and advanced skill levels.
course: Flat, four-corner criterium course with excellent pavement.
registration: Register online at www.usacycling.org or sign up the day of.
notes: These training crits are non-competitive and no prizes will be awarded. Headlights are mandatory for all riders. No restroom facilities are available.
directions:
1550 E 36th St, Tucson, AZ 85713
Southwest corner of Kino Parkway and 36th Street.
